### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">أَوَلَمْ يَعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَبْسُطُ ٱلرِّزْقَ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيَقْدِرُ ۚ إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَـٰتٍ لِّقَوْمٍ يُؤْمِنُونَ</span>

### English

Do they not know that Allah gives abundant or limited provisions to whoever He wills? Surely in this are signs for people who believe.